snippet.title: Best VGM 2008 - Castlevania : Order of Ecclesia - An Empty Tome
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 297 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FjFx5oO-riE

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Castlevania : Order of Ecclesia (2008)
An Empty Tome
Michiru Yamane
